import { Button, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'
import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux'
import axios from 'axios'

const AdminHome = () => {
    // const dispatch = useDispatch()
    // const movieObject = useSelector( state => state.movie.movies)
    const [ movieDetails, setMovieDetails ] = useState({
      movieImageUrl : '', 
      movieVideoUrl : '', 
      movieName : '', 
      ticketCost : '', 
      description : '',
      actorName : '',
      directorName : '',
      startBookingDate : new Date(''),
      endBookingDate : new Date('')
    })
    const getMovies = () => {
      axios.get('http://localhost:3040/movies')
      .then( movie => {
        console.log("movies : ",movie)
        setMovieDetails(movie)
    } )
      .catch( err => console.log(err) )
    }
    useEffect(() => {
      getMovies()
    },[])
    return(<>
      AdminHome Page
      <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
      <CardMedia
        component="img"
        height="250"
        image="https://w0.peakpx.com/wallpaper/161/966/HD-wallpaper-dulquer-salman-charlie-malayalam-movie.jpg"
        alt="image not found"
      />
      <CardContent>
        {/* <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
          Lizard
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
          Lizards are a widespread group of squamate reptiles, with over 6,000
          species, ranging across all continents except Antarctica
        </Typography> */}
        <Button variant='outlined' color='primary' >View</Button>
        <Button variant='outlined' color='primary' style={{marginLeft : '150px'}}>Book</Button>
      </CardContent>
      {/* <CardActions>
        <Button size="small">Share</Button>
        <Button size="small">Learn More</Button>
      </CardActions> */}
    </Card>
      
    </>)
 }

 export default AdminHome
